            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-6">How We Work Together</h2>
            <ol class="space-y-6">
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Discovery Call (Free)</h3>
                  <p class="text-surface-400 text-sm mt-1">We discuss your needs, goals, and constraints. I'll tell you honestly if Flutter is the right choice.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Scope & Quote</h3>
                  <p class="text-surface-400 text-sm mt-1">Clear specification of features, timeline, and fixed price. No surprises.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Development Sprints</h3>
                  <p class="text-surface-400 text-sm mt-1">Weekly updates with working builds. You see progress, not just promises.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Testing & Polish</h3>
                  <p class="text-surface-400 text-sm mt-1">Thorough testing on real devices, performance optimization, UX refinement.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</span>
