          </section>

          <!-- FAQ -->
          <section class="glass-card p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-white mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Why Flutter instead of native or React Native?</h3>
                <p class="text-surface-400">Flutter offers the best balance of development speed, native performance, and code sharing. One codebase means faster delivery and lower maintenance costs. The UI is pixel-perfect on both platforms.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Do you build for iOS too?</h3>
                <p class="text-surface-400">Yes. I develop Android-first (faster iteration), but the same code runs on iOS. iOS builds require an Apple Developer account on your side for App Store submission.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">What about app maintenance after launch?</h3>
                <p class="text-surface-400">I offer optional maintenance packages. You also get full source code and documentation, so any Flutter developer can continue the work.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Can the app work without internet?</h3>
                <p class="text-surface-400">Absolutely. Offline-first is my specialty. Data syncs automatically when connection returns. Critical for field workers and areas with poor connectivity.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class="space-y-6">
          <div class="glass-card p-6 sticky top-24">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-white mb-4">Ready to Start?</h3>
            <p class="text-surface-400 text-sm mb-6">Let's discuss your project. Free 30-minute discovery call, no obligations.</p>
            <a href={`/${lang}/#contact`} class="btn-primary w-full justify-center mb-4">
              Get in Touch
            </a>
            <div class="text-center">
              <a href={`/${lang}/projects`} class="text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 text-sm transition-colors">
